325
00:22:57.837 --> 00:22:58.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles!</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:22:58.836 --> 00:22:59.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:23:02.635 --> 00:23:03.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be quiet!</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:23:07.793 --> 00:23:09.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: That's one Black Hole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>straight up, right?</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:23:11.752 --> 00:23:12.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Synthale, please.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:23:13.791 --> 00:23:15.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be right with you, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:23:25.948 --> 00:23:27.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark, what about that synthale?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:23:27.548 --> 00:23:28.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just another minute.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:23:33.385 --> 00:23:35.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark?</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:23:34.665 --> 00:23:37.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, Chief, I'm a little busy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>right now.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:23:39.744 --> 00:23:41.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm in no mood for games, Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:23:41.783 --> 00:23:43.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So why don't you give me my drink</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:23:43.863 --> 00:23:46.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or I break every bone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in your worthless little body.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:23:46.902 --> 00:23:49.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, just because your life's</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in shambles right now--</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:23:49.621 --> 00:23:51.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:23:52.021 --> 00:23:54.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One synthale coming right up.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:23:54.939 --> 00:23:55.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:24:22.291 --> 00:24:23.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles?</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:24:24.930 --> 00:24:25.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:24:26.890 --> 00:24:30.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I've never really been gone, have I?</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:24:32.528 --> 00:24:33.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not real.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:24:34.368 --> 00:24:35.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're just in my head.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:24:36.007 --> 00:24:37.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's all I ever was.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:24:38.767 --> 00:24:41.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I'm real to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and that's all that matters.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:24:42.285 --> 00:24:43.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go away.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:24:43.845 --> 00:24:47.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your friend. You need me.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:24:48.243 --> 00:24:50.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the last thing I need.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:24:50.403 --> 00:24:53.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're wrong, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You need me, now more than ever.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:25:21.674 --> 00:25:22.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:25:23.593 --> 00:25:24.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to work.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:25:25.432 --> 00:25:30.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, as your friend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have to tell you I'm worried about you.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:25:35.349 --> 00:25:37.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be. I'm home.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:25:38.300 --> 00:25:38.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm working</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:25:39.548 --> 00:25:41.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and for the first time in as long</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as I can remember</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:25:42.067 --> 00:25:42.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel good.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:25:44.227 --> 00:25:45.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why am I here?</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:25:45.346 --> 00:25:48.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sisko to O'Brien.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please report to my office.</i></c.bg_transparent>

362
00:25:48.345 --> 00:25:49.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On my way.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:25:50.465 --> 00:25:51.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I don't know why you're here</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:25:52.704 --> 00:25:53.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I don't care.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:26:07.340 --> 00:26:08.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have a seat.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:26:15.817 --> 00:26:19.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand you had a confrontation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Dr. Bashir yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:26:20.456 --> 00:26:21.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that's a...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That was nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:26:22.255 --> 00:26:23.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not according to Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:26:24.295 --> 00:26:27.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We had a little argument.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Julian and I are always arguing.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:26:27.734 --> 00:26:30.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to Constable Odo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you also had an incident with Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:26:31.293 --> 00:26:32.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did that little?</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:26:34.732 --> 00:26:37.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, sir, I may have let things get</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little out of hand, but...</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:26:38.490 --> 00:26:39.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't happen again.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:26:39.770 --> 00:26:40.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm...</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:26:41.330 --> 00:26:44.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Bashir also tells me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've stopped seeing your counselor.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:26:45.900 --> 00:26:46.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, I've been very busy lately--</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:26:46.568 --> 00:26:48.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The agreement was that you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were going to see a counselor</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:26:48.927 --> 00:26:49.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a regular basis.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:26:51.406 --> 00:26:52.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're right.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:26:52.686 --> 00:26:54.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll make an appointment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to go see him tomorrow.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:26:54.845 --> 00:26:56.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll see him today.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:26:57.445 --> 00:26:58.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:26:59.484 --> 00:27:00.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have a lot of work to do today, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:27:01.204 --> 00:27:02.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The work can wait.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:27:04.323 --> 00:27:06.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As of now, you're relieved of duty.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:27:06.842 --> 00:27:08.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to report to Counselor Telnorri</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:27:09.041 --> 00:27:11.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and begin attending</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>daily counseling sessions</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:27:11.560 --> 00:27:13.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for as long as he thinks it's advisable.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:27:14.520 --> 00:27:16.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, you're blowing this all</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of proportion.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:27:16.998 --> 00:27:18.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know that's not true.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:27:18.838 --> 00:27:20.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to you on Argratha</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:27:20.638 --> 00:27:22.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>affected you a lot more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than you're willing to admit</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:27:23.077 --> 00:27:24.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's not going to get better overnight</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:27:24.876 --> 00:27:26.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>no matter how much you want it to.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:27:27.396 --> 00:27:28.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need help.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:27:29.595 --> 00:27:30.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:27:31.915 --> 00:27:36.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you as a personal favor to me.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Give me one more chance.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:27:39.392 --> 00:27:40.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I could.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:27:42.831 --> 00:27:43.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But right now</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:27:43.951 --> 00:27:46.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in the judgment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this station's Chief Medical Officer</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:27:47.230 --> 00:27:51.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you're unfit for duty</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>which means you're on medical leave</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:27:51.695 --> 00:27:52.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>effective immediately</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:27:52.428 --> 00:27:54.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and if you don't begin attending</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>counseling sessions</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:27:55.027 --> 00:27:55.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a regular basis</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:27:56.684 --> 00:27:58.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and cooperating in every</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>other way with your physician</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:27:59.067 --> 00:28:00.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will have no choice</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:28:00.426 --> 00:28:02.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but to have you confined</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:28:02.665 --> 00:28:03.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that clear?</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:28:05.654 --> 00:28:06.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:28:09.383 --> 00:28:11.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dismissed.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:28:20.020 --> 00:28:22.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, I was just about to head down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Replimat...</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:28:22.940 --> 00:28:24.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not now, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:28:27.458 --> 00:28:28.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Promenade.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:28:36.295 --> 00:28:37.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What the hell did you say to him?</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:28:38.561 --> 00:28:39.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take it you talked to Captain Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:28:39.934 --> 00:28:40.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I talked to him, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:28:41.414 --> 00:28:44.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He relieved me of duty.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's for the best, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:28:44.541 --> 00:28:45.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know what's best for me?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:28:46.532 --> 00:28:48.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have no idea what I've been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>going through!</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:28:48.451 --> 00:28:51.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're right. You were alone in that cell.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I wasn't there with you.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:28:51.531 --> 00:28:54.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't see what they did to you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I do know you suffered</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:28:54.283 --> 00:28:56.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that you're still suffering now,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm trying to help.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:28:56.729 --> 00:28:58.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never asked for your help.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:28:58.528 --> 00:29:02.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You didn't need to ask.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your doctor and your friend.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:29:02.327 --> 00:29:03.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>EE'CHAR: You should listen to him, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:29:04.207 --> 00:29:06.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He cares about you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just like I did.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:29:06.566 --> 00:29:09.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't make the same mistake with him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you did with me.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:29:10.885 --> 00:29:12.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you get it?</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:29:13.004 --> 00:29:15.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not my friend! Not anymore!</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:29:16.523 --> 00:29:18.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The O'Brien that was your friend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>died in that cell!</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:29:19.402 --> 00:29:20.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not dead.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:29:21.442 --> 00:29:23.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He just needs a little help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:29:24.417 --> 00:29:25.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay away from me.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:29:26.360 --> 00:29:28.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your help,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your friendship</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:29:29.199 --> 00:29:30.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just want to be left alone!</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:29:34.278 --> 00:29:36.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where are you going?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I told you to go away!</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:29:36.437 --> 00:29:39.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, please, don't do this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Go back there and talk to him.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:29:39.756 --> 00:29:40.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He wants to help you.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:29:40.796 --> 00:29:42.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Like you did?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:29:42.716 --> 00:29:45.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We're both your friends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah, and look what happened to you.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:29:46.514 --> 00:29:47.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Habitat Ring.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:29:54.711 --> 00:29:57.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, sooner or later</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll have to tell someone about me.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:29:57.751 --> 00:29:58.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like hell I will.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:30:00.314 --> 00:30:02.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't run from me forever.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:30:03.749 --> 00:30:04.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're dead</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:30:04.948 --> 00:30:06.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so why don't you go away</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and leave me alone?</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:30:07.508 --> 00:30:09.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want me to leave?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll leave!</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:30:09.587 --> 00:30:10.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Send me away!</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:30:12.079 --> 00:30:12.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:30:12.426 --> 00:30:15.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I keep coming back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's because some part of you</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:30:15.505 --> 00:30:16.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>keeps bringing me here!</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:30:31.941 --> 00:30:34.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, Julian's been trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to contact you for an hour.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:30:34.540 --> 00:30:37.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where have you been?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Walking. Thinking.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:30:37.299 --> 00:30:40.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know. I heard. I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:30:40.594 --> 00:30:43.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I know how much your work means to you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Try telling that to Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:30:44.537 --> 00:30:46.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, come see what I drew.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:30:47.416 --> 00:30:50.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Not now, honey, okay?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm sure it's only temporary.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:30:50.375 --> 00:30:52.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be back at work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before you know it.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:30:52.815 --> 00:30:53.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, you have to come see.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:30:53.893 --> 00:30:55.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, can we talk about this later?</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:30:55.654 --> 00:30:57.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Daddy, come on!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Not now.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:30:57.493 --> 00:31:00.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Please, Daddy, please!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I said not now, right?</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:31:00.292 --> 00:31:02.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said not!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Miles! What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:31:03.971 --> 00:31:06.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, shh, shh.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:31:08.889 --> 00:31:09.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't mean to...</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:31:09.969 --> 00:31:11.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shh.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:31:12.888 --> 00:31:14.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:32:35.623 --> 00:32:36.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief?</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:32:39.982 --> 00:32:42.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get out of here, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:32:43.301 --> 00:32:44.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want to do this, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:32:46.420 --> 00:32:47.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The hell I don't.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:32:50.219 --> 00:32:52.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I don't claim to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you're going through</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:32:52.658 --> 00:32:55.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but whatever it is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's not worth dying for.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:32:57.937 --> 00:32:59.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand at all.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:33:01.695 --> 00:33:02.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not doing this for me.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:33:04.958 --> 00:33:08.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm doing it to protect Keiko and Molly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and everyone else in this station.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:33:09.453 --> 00:33:11.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Protect us from what?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-From me.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:33:14.652 --> 00:33:16.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not the man I used to be.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:33:18.427 --> 00:33:19.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm dangerous.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:33:23.809 --> 00:33:25.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I nearly hit Molly today.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:33:26.209 --> 00:33:28.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All she wanted was a little attention</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:33:28.928 --> 00:33:30.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I nearly hit her.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:33:31.566 --> 00:33:32.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:33:34.806 --> 00:33:37.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a good man, Miles Edward O'Brien</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:33:38.444 --> 00:33:40.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and whatever it is you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've done wrong</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:33:40.444 --> 00:33:41.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you don't deserve to die.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:33:42.204 --> 00:33:43.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sound like Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:33:44.403 --> 00:33:45.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who's Ee'Char?</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:33:48.362 --> 00:33:51.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's... not real.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:33:54.960 --> 00:33:56.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's just a memory, that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:33:57.319 --> 00:33:59.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A memory from Argratha?</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:34:00.794 --> 00:34:02.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who was he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Another prisoner? A guard?</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:34:04.381 --> 00:34:05.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was my cell mate.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:34:06.676 --> 00:34:08.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told me you were alone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in that cell.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:34:09.370 --> 00:34:10.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Twenty years with no one to talk to.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:34:18.192 --> 00:34:23.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was at the end, a week... two maybe.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:34:26.590 --> 00:34:27.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But the rest of the time...</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:34:29.789 --> 00:34:30.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:34:33.228 --> 00:34:34.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to him?</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:34:38.946 --> 00:34:40.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( distant yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:34:40.706 --> 00:34:41.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah...</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:34:42.065 --> 00:34:43.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why'd you do that?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:34:49.424 --> 00:34:50.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't helping.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:34:51.782 --> 00:34:53.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need to concentrate more.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:34:53.782 --> 00:34:57.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter how much I concentrate.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still starving.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:34:58.861 --> 00:35:00.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:35:01.206 --> 00:35:02.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So am I.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:35:03.499 --> 00:35:05.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sure there's nothing left?</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:35:05.419 --> 00:35:08.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not unless you have a hiding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>place I don't know about.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:35:08.497 --> 00:35:11.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ate the last of the food</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I put away a week ago.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:35:14.962 --> 00:35:15.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should have stockpiled more.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:35:16.815 --> 00:35:18.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should have prepared for this.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:35:19.015 --> 00:35:21.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've never let us go this long</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without food before.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:35:22.213 --> 00:35:27.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe they've forgotten about us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or just decided to finally let us die.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:35:30.850 --> 00:35:31.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then we die.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:35:32.810 --> 00:35:35.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARGRATHI: ( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>over PA </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>) </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>All offenders</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>prepare for dormancy period.</i></c.bg_transparent>

517
00:35:35.770 --> 00:35:38.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Any offender still active</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>during the dormancy period</i></c.bg_transparent>

518
00:35:38.329 --> 00:35:39.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>will be disciplined.</i></c.bg_transparent>

519
00:35:39.449 --> 00:35:42.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Illumination will be suspended</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>in 20 seconds.</i></c.bg_transparent>

520
00:35:43.767 --> 00:35:44.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:35:45.447 --> 00:35:46.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to sleep.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:35:46.966 --> 00:35:51.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How can you sleep at a time like this?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Maybe I'll dream about food.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:35:53.404 --> 00:35:54.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're crazy.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:35:54.764 --> 00:35:55.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No...</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:35:57.043 --> 00:35:58.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just hungry.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:35:59.837 --> 00:36:00.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARGRATHI: ( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>over PA </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i></i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dormancy period initiated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

527
00:36:51.947 --> 00:36:52.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:36:56.665 --> 00:36:58.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You pretended to be my friend</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:36:58.945 --> 00:37:01.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and all the time you were holding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out on me.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:37:01.343 --> 00:37:03.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now who's acting crazy?</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:37:09.382 --> 00:37:12.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After everything I've done for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you ungrateful...</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:37:27.896 --> 00:37:29.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( bones crunching )</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:37:41.052 --> 00:37:42.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:37:43.412 --> 00:37:44.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You...</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:37:45.691 --> 00:37:48.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were saving it for both of us.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:37:55.288 --> 00:37:56.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:37:58.926 --> 00:38:00.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char, wake up.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:38:12.203 --> 00:38:13.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char... Ee'Char...</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:38:16.801 --> 00:38:18.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You killed him?</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:38:22.279 --> 00:38:23.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The worst part of it was...</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:38:24.599 --> 00:38:28.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The next day, the guards</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>began feeding me again.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:38:30.797 --> 00:38:32.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I killed him for nothing,</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:38:33.317 --> 00:38:35.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for a scrap of bread</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he was going to share with me.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:38:36.475 --> 00:38:38.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it was a mistake. You didn't mean it.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:38:41.273 --> 00:38:42.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I meant it.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:38:43.633 --> 00:38:45.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted him to die.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:38:47.552 --> 00:38:49.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I keep telling myself...</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:38:50.591 --> 00:38:51.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:38:51.951 --> 00:38:53.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't real.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:38:53.870 --> 00:38:54.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But that's a lie.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:38:55.949 --> 00:38:57.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it had been real, if it had been you</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:38:57.829 --> 00:38:58.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>instead of him</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:38:59.388 --> 00:39:01.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it wouldn't have made any difference.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:39:02.292 --> 00:39:05.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was my best friend and I murdered him.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:39:08.386 --> 00:39:12.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When we were growing up,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they used to tell us...</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:39:12.655 --> 00:39:13.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Humanity had evolved</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:39:16.047 --> 00:39:20.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that mankind had outgrown hate and rage.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:39:22.502 --> 00:39:23.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But when it came down to it</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:39:24.981 --> 00:39:29.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I had the chance to show</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no matter what anyone did to me</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:39:29.619 --> 00:39:32.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was still an evolved human being...</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:39:34.458 --> 00:39:35.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I failed.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:39:38.657 --> 00:39:41.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I repaid kindness with blood.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:39:45.454 --> 00:39:47.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was no better than an animal.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:39:47.814 --> 00:39:48.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. No, no, no.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:39:49.293 --> 00:39:50.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>An animal would've killed Ee'Char</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:39:50.813 --> 00:39:53.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and never had a second thought,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never shed a tear</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:39:53.932 --> 00:39:55.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but not you. You hate yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:39:56.851 --> 00:39:59.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You hate yourself so much you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you deserve to die.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:40:00.490 --> 00:40:03.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Argrathi did everything they could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to strip you of your humanity</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:40:04.648 --> 00:40:07.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and in the end, for one brief moment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they succeeded.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:40:08.408 --> 00:40:11.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you can't let that brief moment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>define your entire life.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:40:12.206 --> 00:40:16.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you do, if you pull that trigger</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then the Argrathi will have won.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:40:17.685 --> 00:40:23.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They will have destroyed a good man.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You cannot let that happen, my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:40:37.759 --> 00:40:38.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:40:41.038 --> 00:40:42.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be well, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:41:07.030 --> 00:41:09.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thirty milligrams twice a day.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Take it religiously for a month.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:41:09.310 --> 00:41:11.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And if all goes well</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll experiment with a lower dosage.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:41:11.349 --> 00:41:12.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sure this'll work?</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:41:12.349 --> 00:41:15.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a treatment, not a cure.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It'll prevent hallucinations</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:41:15.547 --> 00:41:17.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>take the edge off the depression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but that's all it'll do.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:41:17.587 --> 00:41:19.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't take away the memories</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or the feelings.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:41:19.706 --> 00:41:20.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean the guilt.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:41:21.306 --> 00:41:22.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, that'll take time.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:41:24.545 --> 00:41:26.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now's the part where you tell me</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:41:26.465 --> 00:41:28.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to start seeing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Counselor Telnorri again.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:41:29.647 --> 00:41:30.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unless you want to talk to me.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:41:31.702 --> 00:41:33.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Telnorri'll be fine.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:41:38.461 --> 00:41:40.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks, Julian... For everything.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:41:41.380 --> 00:41:42.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are friends for?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:41:51.937 --> 00:41:54.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy's home! Daddy's home!</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:42:01.294 --> 00:42:03.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right. Daddy's home.</c.bg_transparent>

